    IVariableList
    This implements a list-like interface for WrGetVariableList and WrSetVariableList.
    WrGetVariableList
    This is basically a wrapper around a hashset.
    WrSetVariableList
    Implements a list of settable variable pairs for use by the WrAsyncSocket or WrBlockingSocket.
    WrVariablePair
    This class holds a variable and value into a `std::pair`/`tuple` like object that can be used by the api classes.
